data.description:
Price Improvement! Open House Tuesday, 11/21 from 12-2pm! 
Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Alma! This spacious 4-bedroom residence sits on a sprawling 2.83-acre m/l lot, offering you the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. With a spacious living room, modern amenities, and delightful outdoor spaces, this property is sure to capture your heart. This home has undergone numerous tasteful updates, including a fully remodeled bathroom, a finished sunroom with its own mini-split unit, a huge pool and deck area, and a large back porch PLUS a wonderfully landscaped firepit/entertainment area, perfect for enjoying the peaceful Arkansas evenings. This home also boasts a new roof as of this year, as well as a tankless water heater. Enjoy the acreage and space while remaining minutes away from Walmart, I-49 & I-40, as well as award-winning Alma schools! Don't wait, schedule your private showing today!
